Unicron/Teufel:



Unicron avoided the  fired at him, blocking most of the other stuff that 
would've hit him with his shield which he quickly estimated to be at 58% 
integrity.  Some other blasts dug into his leg but he ignored the pain.

He fired off five rapid emerald optic blasts down at Hot Rod.  Raising both 
arms, he fired a missile from each.

One at Hot Rod, the other at Iron Raptor (if she's at the battle, if she 
ain't just ignore the second missile).

"Give up, Autobot.  I am greater than anything you can possibly imagine.  I 
defeated the God of Light, Primus.  You are no match for me."

---

Teufel avoided the shots fired upon him, which were mostly base defenses.  He 
raised both arms, firing a missile from each.  Both heading for the Element 
(starship).

His turrets fired ten rapid laser blasts each, a total of twenty rapid laser 
blasts lancing out at Element's (gestalt) legs.  He looked to Unicron to 
check on his situation and right now it seemed alright.  The scanning was 
complete, but he had not been upgraded with the proper technology by the 
Chaos-Bringer, so he could not transform to his copycat mode.
